1
00:00:03,977 --> 00:00:08,974
I was in Odessa in someone's room, 
and I swear this is true.

2
00:00:09,575 --> 00:00:14,687
They had a pet—a white rat 
in the cage in the room.

3
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:20,800
Which made me a little nervous, 
to tell you the truth.

4
00:00:21,072 --> 00:00:23,305
But I was a guest.

5
00:00:23,555 --> 00:00:27,345
[The Rat that Got Mantram]

6
00:00:27,434 --> 00:00:32,056
So I tried to connect with the rat
as best we could.

7
00:00:33,870 --> 00:00:38,045
And a certain delicacy of the fingers

8
00:00:39,239 --> 00:00:42,856
convinced me that rat was a person.

9
00:00:42,856 --> 00:00:46,093
And just looking at each other.

10
00:00:46,093 --> 00:00:51,921
So the next morning 
I gave mantram to someone in that room.

11
00:00:52,819 --> 00:00:54,911
So the rat got mantram.

12
00:00:55,907 --> 00:00:59,652
And then left the world like a few days later.

13
00:01:00,578 --> 00:01:04,828
So what is the Krishna Consciousness movement,
I ask you?

